Instalation

1. change Pythia and HepMC locations in path.inc

2. set up local variables
	source path.inc

3a) Superuser instalation
. enter super user mode
	su

. if there are some problems
	man su
	apt-get install su

. build and install shared library in /usr/local/lib
	make

. leave super user mode
	exit

3b) local instalation
. build library
	make local
